    \begin{block}{Forward Propagation}
        \begin{itemize}
            \item Data flows from input to output layers.
            \item Each layer transforms data using weights and activation functions.
            \item Aim: Minimize loss function to improve prediction.
        \end{itemize}
    \end{block}

